{"ID":"20260609125205-vp2m43t","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609125205-vp2m43t","title":"2022年北京卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609125310"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609125205-c72wgvl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125205-c72wgvl","updated":"20260609125227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"①2013年起，北京加大力度治理大气污染。②2017年，在大气污染防治秋冬季攻坚行动部署会上，北京市委市政府提出空气治理要一微克一微克地去抠，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"由此开展“一微克”攻坚行动"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"综合运用科技、执法、管理等手段"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，精准治理大气污染。③2019年，北京PM2.5年均浓度值首次进入“40+”，创历史新低。④截止2020年底，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"北京市环境空气质量的改善在“十三五”规划目标基础上进一步提高"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，与2013年相比，PM2.5、PM10、二氧化氮、二氧化硫的浓度值均大幅下降。⑤这些治理措施也为2022年的北京贡献了清澈的“冬奥蓝”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125205-syt6gac","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609125205-syt6gac","updated":"20260609125243"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260609125243-a8hwj41","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125243-a8hwj41","updated":"20260609125243"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"(1)下列说法正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609125243-a22bi2f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125243-a22bi2f","updated":"20260609125243"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．②句中的两个画线部分可以互换位置。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125243-hwpgvai","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125243-hwpgvai","updated":"20260609125243"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．③句中的“首次”换为“首先”，句意不变。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125243-74x6yj2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125243-74x6yj2","updated":"20260609125243"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．④句中的“截止”应换为“截至”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125243-y7gvd7f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125243-y7gvd7f","updated":"20260609125243"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．④句中画线的语句没有语病。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125243-5tmylqh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125243-5tmylqh","updated":"20260609125243"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"(2)不改变句意，请用“得益于”改写⑤句，将改写后的答案写在答题卡上。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125205-gu86505","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609125205-gu86505","updated":"20260609125254"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609125254-z38kdt8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125254-z38kdt8","updated":"20260609125254"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"(1)C"}]},{"ID":"20260609125254-2s7y5mg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125254-2s7y5mg","updated":"20260609125254"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"(2)2022年北京清澈的“冬奥蓝”也得益于这些治理措施。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125205-qctyd0u","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609125205-qctyd0u","updated":"20260609125310"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609125310-3l1ulrv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125310-3l1ulrv","updated":"20260609125310"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（1）本题考查学生辨析并修改病句的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125310-u08k891","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125310-u08k891","updated":"20260609125310"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.“②句中的两个画线部分可以互换位置”错误，“由此开展……行动”承接前文北京市委市政府提出的观点“空气治理要一微克一微克地去抠”，而“综合运用……手段”与后文“精准治理大气污染”也是顺承关系。所以“由此开展……行动，综合运用……手段”两个分句不可互换位置，"}]},{"ID":"20260609125310-zxoc11k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125310-zxoc11k","updated":"20260609125310"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.“③句中的‘首次’换为‘首先’，句意不变”错误，“首次”意思是第一次，头一回，指同一事项出现的第一次；“首先”的意思是最早，率先，指的是某一事项出现的时间最早。两词意思不同，更换后句意也不同。所以替换后句意发生改变。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125310-2ov027g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125310-2ov027g","updated":"20260609125310"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D.“④句中画线的语句没有语病”错误，④句中画线的语句“改善……提高”搭配不当，可把“的改善”删掉。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125310-i9bkp80","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125310-i9bkp80","updated":"20260609125310"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125310-1dpff2y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125310-1dpff2y","updated":"20260609125310"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（2）本题考查学生语言表达之句式变换的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125310-zwqnrvh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125310-zwqnrvh","updated":"20260609125310"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目要求不改变句意，用“得益于”改写⑤句。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125310-8bjx8xu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125310-8bjx8xu","updated":"20260609125310"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“得益于”可以做句子的谓语，主语应是“好的结果”，即2022年北京清澈的“冬奥蓝”；宾语应是“这些治理措施”。所以可改写为“2022年北京清澈的‘冬奥蓝’也得益于这些治理措施”。"}]}]}